data.description: Welcome to your own little slice of Philadelphia! The pristine white exterior of this classic row home exudes timeless charm. When you walk into the sun-filled entryway, you’re greeted by an elegant doorway that takes you into a cozy living room complete with a fireplace just waiting to be lit. Walk through the first level into the recently renovated kitchen waiting to welcome its new homeowner. Upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms and an updated bathroom. The finished basement offers endless possibilities; use it as a family room, home office, or an entertainment area. The bathroom in the basement adds convenience and functionality to this lower level space. Near your new neighborhood, you'll enjoy the convenience of nearby schools, parks, shops, and public transportation. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautifully updated Philadelphia home your own. Contact us today to schedule a showing and experience the potential of this remarkable property for yourself!
